metadata.name: SAVE ME
metadata.description:
The art “SAVE ME” is dedicated to victims of the war in Ukraine.
We shall NOT be silent during this horrible war, we must do everything we can to stop this horrible disaster and stand up for justice.

The profit made on the sale of this art will go to victim support of the war in Ukraine.

Image: Hand-painted and digitally retouched
JPEG RGB 32.4MB, 7000x7466px – print quality

Utility: The image is printable in high quality: 60x64cm (max)
